reviewText: This DVD would not play in my DVD player the disk is for another country & wouldn't work hopefully the issue will be resolved & I can get the correct item as this was a gift from their elf on the shelf & they were beyond devasted they couldn't watch the movie on Christmas eve
This DVD would not play in my DVD player. It has the wrong country code. Not made for USA. I even tried changing the code in the DVD player. It still would not play.
